title: Person of Interest - 4x20 'Terra Incognita' - You Stop, You Die
author: POISuit
comment: I just finished this series after stopping watching it back when it was airing after season 3 - and this scene and the finale was so good. This was a beautiful show - makes me miss truly good tv writing
